<p class="ayah 69-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَغَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">overflowed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the water,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَمَلْنَـٰكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We carried you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجَارِيَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sailing (ship).</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>11<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
